# textdomain: mcl_cake
Cake=Torta
With 7 tasty slices! Hunger points: +@1 per slice=
Cakes can be placed and eaten to restore hunger points. A cake has 7 slices. Each slice restores @1 hunger points and @2 saturation points. Cakes will be destroyed when dug or when the block below them is broken.=
Place the cake anywhere, then rightclick it to eat a single slice. You can't eat from the cake when your hunger bar is full.=Posiziona la torta ovunque, mangia una fetta col tasto destro. Se la barra della fame è piena non puoi mangiare una fetta di torta.
